{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","title":"contentInset","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1610","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)contentInset","fragments":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is equal to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"text":", viewport","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"properties such as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"text":" assume a viewport that matches the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map center is effectively shifted downward.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":" whose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"text":" property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the value of this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property may be overridden at any time.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The usage of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"text":" has been deprecated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use the map view’s property ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"},{"text":"instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setContentInset:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s logical viewport."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","title":"automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/automaticallyadjustscontentinset","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A boolean value that indicates if whether the map view should automatically"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"adjust its content insets.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/contentInset":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s logical viewport."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"contentInset"}}}